-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
P1               0       4       3        10           0         4         0           4         0       no
P2               1       2       2         7           5         7         4           6         4       no
P3               5       3       2        20           7        10         2           5         2       no
P4               2       1       1         5           4         5         2           3         2       no

