-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
P1               0       4       3        10           0         4         0           4         0       no
P2               1       2       2         7           5         7         4           6         4       no
P3               5       3       2        20           7        10         2           5         2       no
P4               2       1       1         5           4         5         2           3         2       no

Summary metrics:
  Makespan              : 10
  Total busy time       : 10
  CPU utilization       : 100.00%
  Throughput            : 0.40 processes/unit-time
  Average waiting time  : 2.00
  Average turnaround    : 4.50
  Average response time : 2.00
  Deadline misses       : 0 / 4


========================================================
Round Robin
========================================================
Preemptive. Each ready process gets at most quantum=3 time units per turn. Arrivals at a time-slice boundary are queued before the preempted process.

Execution timeline:
  [ 0,  3)  P1
  [ 3,  5)  P2
  [ 5,  6)  P4
  [ 6,  7)  P1
  [ 7, 10)  P3

Compact Gantt view:
  |0 P1 |3 P2 |5 P4 |6 P1 |7 P3 |10

Per-process results:
Process        Arr   Burst    Prio  Deadline  FirstStart    Finish   Waiting  Turnaround  Response   Missed
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
P1               0       4       3        10           0         7         3           7         0       no
P2               1       2       2         7           3         5         2           4         2       no
P3               5       3       2        20           7        10         2           5         2       no
P4               2       1       1         5           5         6         3           4         3      yes

Summary metrics:
  Makespan              : 10
  Total busy time       : 10
  CPU utilization       : 100.00%
  Throughput            : 0.40 processes/unit-time
  Average waiting time  : 2.50
  Average turnaround    : 5.00
  Average response time : 1.75
  Deadline misses       : 1 / 4


==================== POLICY COMPARISON ====================
Policy                              Avg Wait  Avg Turnaround      Avg Resp    Misses      Util %
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
FCFS - First Come First Served          2.25            4.75          2.25         1      100.00
SJF - Shortest Job First                2.00            4.50          2.00         0      100.00
Priority Scheduling                     2.00            4.50          2.00         0      100.00
Round Robin                             2.50            5.00          1.75         1      100.00

Interpretation hints:
  - Lower waiting/turnaround time is usually better for batch-style workloads.
  - Lower response time is important for interactive workloads.
  - Round Robin often improves response time, but can increase turnaround time.
  - Deadline misses show whether a policy is suitable for time-bound workloads.
